4 THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the House of Representatives of the
5 Legislature of Louisiana does hereby commend Alpha Kappa Alpha Sorority, Incorporated,
6 Zeta Lambda Omega Chapter, on the occasion of its one hundred eighteenth Founders' Day
7 and seventy-first Charter Day; does hereby extend enduring appreciation for the chapter's
8 longstanding service to the citizens of Rapides Parish and the state of Louisiana; and does
9 hereby extend sincere wishes for the continued success of its members in their mission of
10 service to all mankind.
